OL,3,CCaroline Glachan: Trio found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering schoolgirl in 1996
OL,6,FTwo men and one woman have been found
OL,7,Fguilty of murdering a schoolgirl in
OL,8,FWest Dunbartonshire 27 years ago.
OL,10,FThe body of 14-year-old Caroline
OL,11,FGlachan was found on the banks of the
OL,12,FRiver Leven on August 25, 1996.
OL,14,FOn Thursday, Robert O'Brien, 45,
OL,15,FAndrew Kelly and Donna Marie Brand,
OL,16,Fboth 44, were convicted of her murder,
OL,17,Fafter a trial at the High Court in
OL,18,FGlasgow.
